<h1>Articles</h1>

Our Blog has <%= Article.public_count %> articles and counting! <br>
Our Blog Articles have <%= Comment.public_count %> comments and counting! <br>

<ul>
    <% @articles.each do |article| %>
        <% unless article.archived? %>
        <li>
            <%= link_to article.title, article %>
        </li>
        <% end %>
    <% end %>
</ul>

<%= link_to "New Article", new_article_path %>